text: Heidenlöcher is a 1986 Austrian-West German drama movie directed by Wolfram Paulus. It starred Albert Paulus, Rolf Zacher, Florian Pircher, Helmut Vogel, Matthias Aichhorn. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1986 drama movies Category:Austrian drama movies Category:German drama movies
